).

Pedipalpus.
Tr with two geminate ventral setiferous tubercles. Fe with a ventral basal and a mesal apical setiferous tubercle. Pa unarmed (
Fig. 6A
).Ti with two rows of setiferous tubercles: four (IiIi) ventro-mesal; (IiIi) ventro-ectal (
